# OpenRobOps configs

This folder contains YAML files that need to be applied to OpenRobOps to configure data sources, 
actions and other settings in OpenRobOps specific to this flatland simulation.

Note: To apply configs, use InOrbit's CLI. First set up `INORBIT_CLI_API_KEY` and
`INORBIT_CLI_URL` (e.g. http://oro.example.com/api) environment variables, then:
```
inorbit apply -f config.yaml
```
